ide for linguists interested in the language.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Jan 2023) 4aIranische Sprachen. 4aLinguistik. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh  aLinguistics, Central Asian Studies, Iranian Linguistics.1 aDodykhudoeva, Leyli R., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHasanova, Dilia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHassan Sulton, Mirzo, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aIdo, Shinji, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aIdo, Shinji, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aKoohkan, Sepideh, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMahmoodi-Bakhtiari, Behrooz, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aMofidi, Roohollah, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNafchi, Negin Mohammadi, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPower, Justin M., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRzehak, Lutz, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2023 Part 1z978311117578208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDe Gruyter Mouton eBook Package 2023z97831112057930 cEPUBz97831106195390 cprintz978311061940940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311062279940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110622799423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110622799/original  a978-3-11-117578-2  DG Plus DeG Package 2023 Part 1b2023  a978-3-11-120579-3  De Gruyter Mouton eBook Package 2023b2023  aEBA_CL_LS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  